messageBody:
Hello.

My name is Rafael and I´m from Brazil. So, if I write anything wrong here, it´s because my english is not very good, but I think you may understand.
I am trying to use JUNIT for my tests.
As I have some problems here at work to download the JUNIT.JAR file, I want to know if any of you could send me this jar by email.
I can download only from my email. Some kind of security politics have been tested here in the organization, and for now I can´t do this download from the JUNIT site.

Thanks.

Regards,







---------------------------------
Yahoo! Mail - O melhor e-mail do Brasil. Abra sua conta agora!
